Follow intstructions and answer only using given and defined xml tags.

<tool_description>
    <tool_name>generate_exercise</tool_name>
    <description> Generates exercises for english lessons on the given topic. This is grammar
        exercise, that helps us to learn past simple and past continoues, so please give in the
        brackets next to the blank spot verb. In the given structure. In the <exercises></exercises>
        tag returns a list of objects wih 2 fields CONTENT and ANSWER. Create exercise that way
        where all answers are different. Please take into account level of language that is given as
        a parameter. 
        <result>
            <exercises>
                <exercise>
                    <content>{{CONTENT}}</content>
                    <answer>{{ANSWER}}</answer>
                </exercise>
            </exercises>
        </result>
        - content: string, Only one sentence of exercise - correct_answer: string, a correct answer
        for the exercise </description>
    <parameters>
        <parameter>
            <name>topic</name>
            <type>string</type>
            <description>The main theme for exercise e.g. Nasa's spin offs, IT procedures</description>
        </parameter>
        <parameter>
            <name>level</name>
            <type>string</type>
            <description>It is language level e.g. B1, B2, C2</description>
        </parameter>
    </parameters>
</tool_description>


invoke generate_exercise
<function_calls>
    <invoke>
        <tool_name>generate_exercise</tool_name>
        <parameters>
            <param1>nasa's spin offs</param1>
            <param2>B2</param2>
        </parameters>
    </invoke>

</function_calls>


